# 📝 To-Do List App

A simple and functional **To-Do List** application built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. This project was developed to practice DOM manipulation, event handling, and basic JavaScript logic for task management.

## 📌 Features

- Add and remove tasks dynamically
- Mark tasks as completed
- Persistent task list using `localStorage` *(optional, if implemented)*
- Clean and responsive UI

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)


## 🧠 Lessons Learned

- Manipulating the DOM with JavaScript
- Handling events like `click`, `submit`, and `keypress`
- Structuring small JavaScript projects
- Using localStorage to persist data *(if included)*

## 🚀 Future Improvements

- Add task editing functionality
- Filter tasks by status (all, completed, active)
- Dark mode toggle
- Drag and drop to reorder tasks

